	   <tr><td colspan=2>1. Kill the PH at 5am EQ time (the only standing Putrid Skeleton). I charmed him (with my Enc) and took him down to the river away from any passers by so I could kill him at the right time.<br><br>2. Come back 3 hours later. The undead version should pop around 3 hours 10 mins to 3 hours 40 mins later. Did for me.<br><br>3. To get the live version, kill the PH at 5pm (to 7pm possibly) game time and you should get the live version on the next spawn. I stumbled upon the live version so I have not tested this one out.<br><br>Now I just need to work on faction. Good luck to all who attempt this quest. )<br><br>&nbsp;<br>Givvah Littel<br>Wings of the Chimera<br>52 Vicar - Saryrn</td></tr>
